   "source": [
    "By Fermat's little theorem:\n",
    "$$ a^{p-1} \\equiv 1 \\pmod{p} $$\n",
    "and so we have:\n",
    "$$ a^{p-2} * a = 1 \\pmod{p} $$\n",
    "so $a^{p-2} \\pmod{p}$ is the modular inverse of $a$."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "a = 3\n",
    "p = 13\n",
    "a**(p-2) % p"
   ]
  }
